column2: SELECT top # m.ra AS ra1, m.DEC AS dec1, stack.ra AS ra, stack.dec AS dec, stack.psfMag_u AS umag, stack.psfMagErr_u AS umagerr, stack.psfMag_g AS gmag, stack.psfMagErr_g AS gmagerr, stack.psfMag_r AS rmag, stack.psfMagErr_r AS rmagerr, stack.psfMag_i AS imag, stack.psfMagErr_i AS imagerr, stack.psfMag_z AS zmag, stack.psfMagErr_z AS zmagerr, stack.mode AS mode, stack.type AS type, stack.flags AS flags, stack.clean AS clean, stack.probPSF AS probPSF, stack.nChild AS nChild, stack.cModelMag_u AS cModelMag_u, stack.cModelMagErr_u AS cModelMagErr_u, stack.cModelMag_g AS cModelMag_g, stack.cModelMagErr_g AS cModelMagErr_g, stack.cModelMag_r AS cModelMag_r, stack.cModelMagErr_r AS cModelMagErr_r, stack.cModelMag_i AS cModelMag_i, stack.cModelMagErr_i AS cModelMagErr_i, stack.cModelMag_z AS cModelMag_z, stack.cModelMagErr_z AS cModelMagErr_z, stack.extinction_u AS extinction_u, stack.extinction_g AS extinction_g, stack.extinction_r AS extinction_r, stack.extinction_i AS extinction_i, stack.extinction_z AS extinction_z FROM MyDB.panstarrs_qso AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS stack ON n.objid = stack.objID
